@NODE 0.1. "What is it"

 What IS it ???
 ==============

  HAviNg Run a BBs for a while i've been lookIng for sommit a BIT different
 from the Usual bbs log off screen doorz !!! All there seem'd to be was
 a load of add bbs's to logoff !! this was getting a bit boring coz every
 bbs had one and they all mostly look'd the same to me !! aha ! idea !
 Peeps like to slag others off on a wall ! why not a wall wid a difference
 A logoff wall ! ya don't know whats on it till it's too late ! arghhhh
 someone diss'd ya and it's to late to get back it em ! SHIT wait till
 the next call and get ya own back on em ! big time ! and they won't know
 till they have log'd off and it's too late for them to do anything bout it

 the door is installed under the "G" logoff key ! it's simple to understand
 and use ! even the lame "KID" can use it without worry !

 check out the nova-low1.iff and the nova-low3.iff if ya wann have a quick
 butchers at it b4 ya think bout installin it to ya setup


 IMPORTANT INFO !
 ----------------

 this door has been optimized for speed " as everyone knows rexx ain't the
 fastest of languages " so to run the door correct then the "G".info must
 only run the rexx script <Doors:NvA/NoVa-low/runit> if you don't run it
 this way it will instantly lock up !!!!!


@ENDNODE

