@NODE 0.5. "Sysop"

 SysOp CommanDz ....
 ===================

 HokAY ! a special sysop screen has now been add'd to the logoff wall
 it will auto enable the sysop commands for any user that has a security
 access of 250 +  " check nova-low2.iff for a quick view of the screen"

 this menu is about the same as the user menu ! it explaines it's self
 on screen !   2 new commands will appear !

 (V)iew logoff wall ! can't guess what that does ??

 (K)ill a messy on the wall ! ! remove the lame bbs plug that some newby
 sysop has left on the wall ! then it ask's what message ya wanna
 remove. type in the numba then it's deleted and will show ya the new
 saved logoff screen !



